        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer860029958" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6277083265771644958">OH SHIT, IT LOOKS AMAZING. SOME TEASER PHOTOS FOR THE SCORCH TRIALS MOVIE.<br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1426227272i/13990071._SX540_.jpg' width='325' height='200' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1426227599i/13990132._SX540_.jpg' width='325' height='200' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1426227599i/13990133._SX540_.jpg' width='325' height='200' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1426227599i/13990134._SX540_.jpg' width='325' height='200' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1426227599i/13990135._SX540_.jpg' width='325' height='200' alt='description' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/>There&apos;s more but these are the best, WHO ELSE IS EXCITED?</span>
  <span id="freeText6277083265771644958" style="display:none">OH SHIT, IT LOOKS AMAZING. SOME TEASER PHOTOS FOR THE SCORCH TRIALS MOVIE.<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1426227272i/13990071._SX540_.jpg" width="325" height="200" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1426227599i/13990132._SX540_.jpg" width="325" height="200" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1426227599i/13990133._SX540_.jpg" width="325" height="200" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1426227599i/13990134._SX540_.jpg" width="325" height="200" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1426227599i/13990135._SX540_.jpg" width="325" height="200" alt="description" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>There's more but these are the best, WHO ELSE IS EXCITED?</span>
