<li class='cover' id='bookCover_18710190'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18710190-allegiant"><img alt="Allegiant (Divergent, #3)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1395582745l/18710190._SX98_.jpg" />
