<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer5369423269868521197">James is the author of THE MAZE RUNNER trilogy and THE 13TH REALITY series. He also published a series (beginning with A DOOR IN THE WOODS) with a small publisher several years ago. He lives and writes in the Rocky Mountains.</span>

